  "local_port": 38002,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What is the process to get a job at Wipro?",
  "response": "To get a job at Wipro, you can follow these steps:\n\n1. **Research and Explore Opportunities:**\n   Visit the Wipro careers website (careers.wipro.com) to explore the various job opportunities available. You can filter the search by location, job function, and experience level to find a position that suits your skills and interests.\n\n2. **Create a Profile and Apply:**\n   Create a profile on the Wipro careers portal, and upload your resume and other relevant documents. When you find a suitable job opening, apply for it through the portal. Make sure your application is tailored to the specific job requirements.\n\n3. **Prepare for the Selection Process:**\n   Wipro's selection process typically involves several stages, including:\n   \n   - **Aptitude Test:** A written or online test to assess your logical reasoning, quantitative ability, and verbal ability.\n   - **Technical Interview:** An interview to evaluate your technical skills and knowledge related to the job role.\n   - **HR Interview:** An interview to assess your communication skills, personality, and cultural fit within the organization.\n\n   Prepare for these stages by brushing up on your technical skills, practicing aptitude tests, and researching common interview questions.\n\n4. **Attend the Interview:**\n   If your application is shortlisted, you will be invited for an interview. This may be conducted in person, over the phone, or through video conferencing, depending on the job location and other factors. Dress professionally, be punctual, and be prepared to discuss your skills, experiences, and motivation for joining Wipro.\n\n5. **Follow-Up and Await the Offer:**\n   After the interview, send a thank-you email to the interviewer(s) to express your appreciation for the opportunity. Await the outcome of your application, which may take a few weeks. If you are selected, you will receive a job offer from Wipro.\n\n6. **Accept the Offer and Complete Onboarding:**\n   If you receive an offer and decide to accept it, follow the instructions provided by Wipro to complete the onboarding process. This may include submitting additional documentation, attending orientation sessions, and completing any necessary training.\n\nRemember to stay proactive, be persistent, and continuously improve your skills to increase your chances of getting a job at Wipro. Good luck!",
